summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting underground and surface rights distribution easements over portions of Lot 8, Block 9, McKenzie and Dempsey's Lake Addition; Section 13, Township 26 North, Range 3 East, W.M. (being known as Tract 90, The Highlands, according to the unrecorded plat thereof); Lots 15, 16 and 17 in Block 8, Bothwell's Replat of Springbrook; Lots 11 through 20 inclusive, Block 16, State Addition; Lot 1, Hughes Beverly Park; Section 29, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; Parcels A and B of King County Short Plat No. 79-22 AND Parcels A, C and D of King County Short Plat No. 79-21; Lot 60, Pritchard Island Addition; Lots 6, 7 and 8, all in Block 1, Sea Shore 2nd Addition; and placing said easements under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
